    bodyHeadings: {"data": {"ja": "Cash Stuffingとは？5億回再生と現金回帰の心理", "en": "What is Cash Stuffing? 500M views and the return to cash"}, "explanation": {"ja": "なぜ効く？痛税効果と日本の袋分け家計簿", "en": "Why it works: the pain of paying and Japan's envelope budgeting"}, "practice": {"ja": "Cash Stuffingの始め方——3封筒の3ステップ", "en": "How to start Cash Stuffing: 3 envelopes, 3 steps"}, "cta": {"ja": "まとめ：袋が空になる瞬間、家計が見える", "en": "The takeaway: awareness sharpens when the envelope empties"}},
    thumbnail: "/images/posts/005/005-thumbnail.jpg",
