    slug: "004-quiet-luxury",
    title_ja: "ロゴなし・主張なし・それが最高級——「Quiet Luxury（静かな贅沢）」という美意識",
    title_en: "Quiet Luxury: Why the Most Expensive Aesthetic Has Nothing to Prove",
    category: "beauty",
